          "shownifval": "My trip to Flock requires air travel.",
          "split": 2
        },
        "doc_research": {
          "type": "documentation",
          "display_name": "",
          "html": [
            "<p>Please research round trip flights to Boston's Logan Airport for Flock. Note that there is a 2-hour long",
